╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║              ROLE HIERARCHY (Top → Bottom)                   ║
╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║                                                              ║
║   SUPER_ADMIN (Level 5)                                      ║
║   ├── Created via database seed / CLI only                   ║
║   ├── Can create Admins                                      ║
║   ├── Can manage everything                                  ║
║   └── CANNOT be created via API signup                       ║
║                                                              ║
║   ADMIN (Level 4)                                            ║
║   ├── Created by Super Admin only                            ║
║   ├── Can approve/reject agent registrations                 ║
║   ├── Can promote agents to Senior Agent                     ║
║   ├── Can manage commissions, payments                       ║
║   └── CANNOT be self-assigned                                ║
║                                                              ║
║   SENIOR_AGENT (Level 3)                                     ║
║   ├── Promoted by Admin/Super Admin                          ║
║   ├── Can manage own team of agents                          ║
║   ├── Can process refunds                                    ║
║   └── CANNOT be self-assigned                                ║
║                                                              ║
║   AGENT (Level 2)                                            ║
║   ├── Default role on signup                                 ║
║   ├── Requires admin approval to activate                    ║
║   ├── Can manage own customers, bookings                     ║
║   └── CANNOT promote self                                    ║
║                                                              ║
║   JUNIOR_AGENT (Level 1)                                     ║
║   ├── Limited access                                         ║
║   ├── Can only view, cannot delete                           ║
║   └── Training/probation role                                ║
║                                                              ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝